data.title: The Space Between the Notes
data.meta_description: Listen to The Space Between the Notes on Spotify. Brought to you by Bedroomdisco, The Space Between the Notes is a show for music fans who want to hear from the artists they love. Hosted by Sam Walsh, this podcast dives deep into the song-writing processes and personal tastes of your favourite bands and songwriters.  Produced and edited by Sam Walsh Intro/Outro Music by Greig Dickson Logo by Rachel Levy
